{"outcome":{"note":{}},"at":804611634.612146,"detail":"thinking: ## DECOMPOSER Report: Issue #56 — README and Related Docs Audit\n\n### Project Facts\n\n| Fact | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| **Language\/framework** | TypeScript (strict). Frontend: SvelteKit 4 with static adapter. Backend: Node.js 20, SAM (Lambda), Amplify Gen2 |\n| **Repo structure** | npm-workspaces monorepo: `apps\/web`, `apps\/api`, `packages\/sdk`, `amplify\/`, `infra\/`, `scripts\/`, `specs\/`, `sdks\/`, `extensions\/` |\n| **Build\/test** | `npm run check:web` (svelte-check + typecheck), `npm run build:web`, `npm test` (vitest, 264+ tests), `npm run build:sdk` |\n| **Live** | https:\/\/vokda.iknsae.com, API: https:\/\/api.vokda.iksnae.com |\n| **Current scale** | 550 voices, 25 providers, 53 languages, 9 synthesis adapters |\n\n### Architecture of \"docs\" Surface\n\nThree tiers of documentation exist:\n\n1. **Root-level markdown** — `README.md` (public-facing), `CLAUDE.md` (agent instructions; most up-to-date), `IDEA.md` (stale early spec), `PRD.md` (product requirements)\n2. **`docs\/` directory** — 14 markdown files + 3 subdirectories (`constitutions\/ts\/`, `constitutions\/go\/`, `research\/`, `specs\/`)\n3. **No `CHANGELOG.md`** exists despite `docs\/PROVIDER_IDS.md` mandating one\n\n### Discrepancies Found\n\n#### A) README.md is severely outdated (the primary work item)\n\n| Section | What README says | What's actually true |\n|---------|-----------------|---------------------|\n| **Stack** | `SvelteKit (TypeScript)` only | SvelteKit 4 + Amplify Gen2 (Cognito, AppSync, 10 DynamoDB tables) + SAM Synthesis API (3 Lambdas, API Gateway, SQS, S3) |\n| **Repo Layout** | `packages\/shared` placeholder | It's `packages\/sdk` (built TS SDK) |\n| **Repo Layout** | `infra` placeholder | Fully built SAM stack with 9 provider adapters, live at `api.vokda.iksnae.com` |\n| **Repo Layout** | Only 4 top-level dirs listed | Missing `extensions\/`, `specs\/`, `scripts\/`, `sdks\/` |\n| **Quick Start** | Only `npm install` + `npm run dev:web` | Missing `test`, `build:web`, `check:web`, `dev:api`, `amplify:sandbox`, `build:sdk` |\n| **Product Docs** | Lists only 7 docs | Missing: `VISION.md`, `DISCOVERY.md`, `SYNTHESIS_API.md`, `AMPLIFY_SETUP.md`, `GITHUB_SETUP.md`, `VOICE_CATALOG_EXPORT.md`, `voice-discovery-process.md`, plus `constitutions\/`, `research\/`, `specs\/` |\n| **Catalog data** | \"app-owned module (phase 1)\" | 550 voices in static JSON, live API at `\/api\/v1\/voices.json` |\n| **Version** | `0.1.0` (in IDEA.md) | `package.json` says `0.3.0` |\n\n#### B) Internal doc conflicts\n\n| Conflict | Details |\n|----------|---------|\n| **Test count** | `ARCHITECTURE.md` says \"178 unit tests\"; `CLAUDE.md` says \"264 web unit tests + infra test suites\" and `package.json`'s script says \"235 tests\" |\n| **DynamoDB tables** | `ARCHITECTURE.md` diagram says \"12 tbl\" but body lists 10 Amplify + 2 SAM = 12; the body paragraph says \"10 tables\" — the numbers resolve but the text is misleading |\n| **localStorage vs DynamoDB** | `ROADMAP.md` §Known Gaps says \"favorites\/collections still in localStorage\"; `AMPLIFY_BACKEND_GEN2.md` §6 says \"Favorites, collections, collection voices, and cart items now sync to Amplify Data\" — directly contradictory |\n| **voice-discovery-process.md** | Says 130 voices across 8 providers. Reality: 550 voices, 25 providers. This doc is a fossil. |\n| **IDEA.md** | Describes a different project (`voice-market`, `Khaos Studio` schemas) with completely different code paths (`src\/domain\/`, `src\/adapters\/`). Not referenced by any doc. Should be removed or archived. |\n\n#### C) Missing CHANGELOG.md\n\n`PROVIDER_IDS.md` (§Changelog expectation) mandates that any change to provider IDs MUST appear in `CHANGELOG.md`. No such file exists. 25 providers have been added without a changelog entry.\n\n---\n\n### Independently-Buildable Deliverables\n\nI recommend decomposing this into **5 independent deliverables**:\n\n---\n\n**Deliverable 1: Rewrite `README.md` to reflect current project state**\n\nUpdate the Stack, Repo Layout, Quick Start, CI\/CD, and Product Docs sections. Source truth from `CLAUDE.md` and `package.json`. Add missing doc references: VISION, DISCOVERY, SYNTHESIS_API, AMPLIFY_SETUP, GITHUB_SETUP, VOICE_CATALOG_EXPORT, voice-discovery-process, constitutions. Add a doc table similar to CLAUDE.md's format. Update catalog description from \"phase 1\" to actual scale (550 voices, 25 providers, live API).\n\n**Deliverable 2: Resolve contradictory statements between `ROADMAP.md` and `AMPLIFY_BACKEND_GEN2.md`**\n\nOne says localStorage, the other says DynamoDB sync. Determine ground truth (check `apps\/web\/src\/lib\/stores\/app-state.ts` or the Amplify Data wiring) and align both docs. Also fix test count: reconcile 178 (ARCHITECTURE) vs 235 (package.json) vs 264 (CLAUDE).\n\n**Deliverable 3: Archive or delete `voice-discovery-process.md` and `IDEA.md`**\n\n`voice-discovery-process.md` is at 130 voices (pre-dates the 550-voice catalog). `IDEA.md` is a different project (voice-market\/Khaos Studio). Both are noise. If they hold any archival value, move to `docs\/research\/` or `.local\/`. Otherwise remove.\n\n**Deliverable 4: Create `CHANGELOG.md`**\n\n`PROVIDER_IDS.md` mandates it. Seed with the 25 current provider IDs and major milestones visible in `ROADMAP.md` and `CLAUDE.md`'s \"Current State\" section. Establish the format so future provider additions\/deprecations can be recorded.\n\n**Deliverable 5: Add cross-reference consistency across the doc corpus**\n\n- `ARCHITECTURE.md`: fix \"10 tables\" → \"12 tables (10 Amplify + 2 SAM-managed)\", update test count to match reality\n- `ROADMAP.md`: resolve localStorage vs DynamoDB contradiction (depends on Deliverable 2's finding)\n- `AMPLIFY_SETUP.md`: replace `PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL` with `PUBLIC_SYNTHESIS_API_URL` (the actual env var used)\n\n---\n\n### Decision Record","ticketId":"56","id":"56-357","phase":"decompose"}
